<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hi all<BR>
Ok Cobalt is real<BR>
Greaves and vambraces drop in Old Sebilis<BR>
Gloves and the less-common boots drop in Karnors<BR>
The items all drop random off the mobs <BR>
<BR>
Boots and gloves (got gloves myself, and saw-but lost lotto on boots) can fall off of any of the "rare" or named spawns.<BR>
In Karnors this includes Caller and Sentry of Sethys, Skeletal Captain, and some others found inside. At the moment my guild isnt quite ready for a thorough Sebilis tour so less info on legs as of yet, will post more when I get more info.<BR>
